.\", \"from\": 808, \"to\": 900, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He failed on all three of his attempts to jump over the second height of the competition before hanging his head in defeat.\", \"from\": 901, \"to\": 1024, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"One day before his devastating dethroning, he shared a positive message with fans about how much defending his place on the podium meant to him.\", \"from\": 1026, \"to\": 1170, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Tomorrow at 7pm, the race of my life,\\\" hewrote.\", \"from\": 1172, \"to\": 1220, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"A little more than 24h to the one I wish with all my heart I will remember for the rest of my life as one of the best nights ever!\\\"\", \"from\": 1221, \"to\": 1353, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Tamberi's crushed podium dreams were even more heartbreaking for the athlete, who was already bereft afterlosinghis wedding ring in the Seine during the opening ceremony on July 26.\", \"from\": 1355, \"to\": 1536, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1492, \"end\": 1497, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 0.999999868775612, \"rank\": 9.267820807151689e-08, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I love you my love \\u2764\\ufe0f,\\\" hewrotein an apology to his wife.\", \"from\": 1538, \"to\": 1596, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"May it be a good omen for returning home with an even bigger gold.\\\"\", \"from\": 1597, \"to\": 1665, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Breaking News Intern  josephine.walker@thedailybeast.com  Got a tip?\", \"from\": 1667, \"to\": 1735, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Send it to The Daily Beasthere.\", \"from\": 1736, \"to\": 1767, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"ADVERTISEMENT  ADVERTISEMENT\", \"from\": 1769, \"to\": 1797, \"entities\": []}]}"